msgstr ""
":attr:`~Rational.numerator` 和 :attr:`~Rational.denominator` 值应为 "
":class:`Integral` 的实例并且应当是具有 :attr:`~Rational.denominator` 正值的最低项。"

#: ../../library/numbers.rst:72 ../../library/numbers.rst:76
msgid "Abstract."
